== Chapter 1: Ragnar ==

=== Overview ===

Ragnar is a soldier of Burland sent to investigate missing children.

'''Playable Characters:'''
* Ragnar McRyan (soldier)
* Healie (temporary NPC ally)

'''Key Locations:'''
* Burland Castle
* Izmit
* Loch Tower
* Children's hideout

=== Objectives ===

# Speak with King of Burland
# Travel to Izmit village
# Investigate children disappearances
# Find and rescue the children
# Defeat chapter boss

== Chapter 2: Alena ==

=== Overview ===

Princess Alena escapes her castle seeking adventure, accompanied by her tutor Brey and priest Cristo.

'''Playable Characters:'''
* Princess Alena (martial artist)
* Brey (mage)
* Cristo (priest)

'''Key Locations:'''
* Santeem Castle
* Surene
* Tempe
* Frenor
* Endor

=== Objectives ===

# Escape Santeem Castle
# Visit villages for clues
# Enter the tournament at Endor
# Win the tournament
# Return to discover castle empty

== Chapter 3: Taloon ==

=== Overview ===

Taloon is a merchant with dreams of owning his own shop. This chapter focuses on earning money and business.

'''Playable Characters:'''
* Taloon (merchant)

'''Key Locations:'''
* Lakanaba
* Bonmalmo (has weapon shop)
* Endor
* Cave to Endor

=== Objectives ===

# Work at Lakanaba weapon shop
# Earn money through various means
# Travel to Endor
# Establish own shop
# Fund tunnel construction

=== Unique Mechanics ===

* Work at shop counter for wages
* Sell items for profit
* Chapter focuses on gold acquisition

== Chapter 4: Mara and Nara ==

=== Overview ===

Sisters seeking revenge for their father's murder by the alchemist Balzack.

'''Playable Characters:'''
* Mara (dancer/mage)
* Nara (fortune teller/priest)
* Orin (temporary ally)

'''Key Locations:'''
* Monbaraba
* Haville
* Keeleon Castle
* Aktemto Mine

=== Objectives ===

# Learn about Balzack's location
# Find ally Orin
# Infiltrate Keeleon
# Confront Balzack
# Chapter ends with unfinished revenge

== Chapter 5: The Hero ==

=== Overview ===

The main chapter where all characters unite to save the world.

'''Starting Characters:'''
* Hero (player-named protagonist)

'''Recruited Characters:'''
* Ragnar (Burland)
* Alena, Brey, Cristo (Santeem)
* Taloon (Endor/Lakanaba)
* Mara and Nara (Monbaraba)

=== Key Events ===

# Hero's village destroyed
# Travel the world recruiting allies
# Collect Zenithian equipment
# Confront Necrosaro
# Final battle

=== Wagon System ===

Chapter 5 introduces the wagon:
* Carry up to 8 characters
* 4 active in battle
* Swap characters during battle
* Wagon characters gain partial EXP

